ed="T" n="0750a14"/><persName key="A009958">釋從隱</persName>，姓<name>劉</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000023795"><placeName>洛陽</placeName><placeName>三鄉</placeName></placeName>人也。丱年<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g635"/>敏慧，誓<lb
ed="T" n="0750a15"/>欲出塵，二親既聽，乃投本邑<placeName key="PL000000023767">竹閣院</placeName>，依師<lb
ed="T" n="0750a16"/>誦習，陶練靈府。尋於<placeName key="PL000000023260">嵩陽</placeName>受戒畢，就<placeName key="PL000000023817">長水</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0750a17"/>聽采<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1058"/>，纔歷數年，克<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g560"/>通《百法》<ptr target="#n1274"/>、《中觀》<ptr target="#n1551"/>、《彌陀》<ptr target="#n1179"/>三經論<lb
ed="T" n="0750a18"/>焉。而<persName key="A009885">諲<roleName>師</roleName></persName>年老，深許<persName key="A009958">隱</persName>之博達性相<ptr type="glossary" target="#g583"/>。後於<lb
ed="T" n="0750a19"/><placeName key="PL000000023571">洛布金院</placeName>赴請敷演。至<placeName key="PL000000057656">後唐</placeName><date notBefore-iso="+0934-06-05" key="j20623522063248" notAfter-iso="+0936-11-17"><name>清泰</name>中</date>，<persName key="A009885">諲</persName>付<lb
ed="T" n="0750a20"/>講座，日為眾三登法席。夏中<ptr type="glossary" target="#g61"/>長晷<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1266"/>，覽藏經<lb
ed="T" n="0750a21"/>一袟，精進苦節，人無與比。<date from-iso="+0949-02-06" key="j20677122067741" to-iso="+0949-03-07"><name>乾祐</name>二年正月</date>，示<lb
ed="T" n="0750a22"/>疾而終，俗壽五十三，僧臘三十二。乃依<placeName key="PL000000048207">天<lb
ed="T" n="0750a23"/>竺</placeName>法火化，收合真體，圓淨堪愛，門人樹塔，<lb
ed="T" n="0750a24"/>至今存焉。次有<placeName key="PL000000023804"><placeName>長水縣</placeName><placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0750002"/>縣泉院<anchor xml:id="end0750002"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1267"/></placeName></placeName><persName key="A009963">釋夢江</persName>者，<lb
ed="T" n="0750a25"/>姓<name>楊</name>氏，<ref target="#PL000000023817" type="place">本邑</ref>人也。神彩灑落，超拔凡態，遂<lb
ed="T" n="0750a26"/>願出家，恒誦《仁王》<ptr target="#n198"/>、《般若》。進具後講《百法論》。<lb
ed="T" n="0750a27"/><date notBefore-iso="+0934-06-05" key="j20623522063248" notAfter-iso="+0936-11-17"><name>清泰</name>中</date><placeName key="PL000000023667"><placeName>龍門</placeName><placeName>廣化寺</placeName></placeName>請為眾開演，遇<ref type="person" target="#A006578">帝</ref>幸<ref target="#PL000000023667" type="place">其<lb
ed="T" n="0750a28"/>寺</ref>宣問<ptr type="glossary" target="#g779"/>，妙辯天逸，悅可上心，時於御前賜<lb
ed="T" n="0750a29"/>紫袈裟，確乎<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1268"/>不受。訓導二十餘年，講罷行道<pb ed="T" n="0750b" xml:id="T50.2061.0750b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0750b01"/><anchor xml:id="beg0750sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0750sgsz1"/>佛，日唯一食。慈忍於物，罕逢慍色。<placeName key="PL000000057658">周</placeName><date from-iso="+0956-02-20" key="j20702822070635" to-iso="+0957-02-07"><name>顯<lb
ed="T" n="0750b02"/>德</name>三年</date>疾終，緇素悲慕，為其建塔矣。</p>
